gomodel:SYNGO_569  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: WAVE3 over-expression decreases spine numbers in hippocampal neutrons (11-14DIV).\n\n9/10/2017 Pim\n- Fig.4 WAVE3 is shown to localize to the edge of Rac-activity induced lamellipodia.\n- Fig.5 The F-actin content of WAVE3 transfected cells increases\nThis shows that WAVE3 is also involved in actin related modifications.. Experimental description: 9/10/2017 Pim\nOE protein is of mouse species: 'Mouse brain was used to prepare cDNA from which WAVE1, WAVE3, and Nck1, \"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2094-7491" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4419-210X" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1190-4481" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9848-0262" ;
        dc:date           "2017-10-09" ;
